<!-- Header -->
<header>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12">
        <img class="img-responsive" src="<%= asset_path( 'bowiebot.png' ) %>" alt="">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <span class="name">BowieIpsum</span>
          <hr class="star-light">
          <span class="skills"><%= @tagline %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Generate Ipsum Section -->
<section id="generate-ipsum">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h2>generate ipsum</h2>
        <hr class="star-primary">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-4 generate-ipsum-form">
        <div class="ipsum-control">
          <%= button_to "Generate Ipsum", generate_ipsum_path, form_class: "form-horizontal", class: "btn btn-success btn-md btn-block generate-ipsum-button" %>
          <%= button_to "Remove Ipsum", "#",  form_class: "form-horizontal", class: "btn btn-danger btn-md btn-block remove-ipsum-button", role: "button" %>
        </div>

        <div class="add-song form-group">
          <h3>Add a new song to the dictionary</h3>
          <%= form_for @song, html: {class: "form-inline"} do |f| %>
            <%= f.label :title, class: "form-label" %>:
            <%= f.text_field :title, class: "form-control" %>
            <%= f.submit "Add Song", class: "form-control btn btn-default btn-md" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <% flash.each do |name, msg| -%>
          <%= content_tag :div, msg, class: name %>
        <% end -%>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-8 generate-ipsum-item">
        <div class="ipsum-well">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About Section -->
<section class="success" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <hr class="star-light">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-2">
        <p>Hi, I'm Bri. I have an affinity for David Bowie, twitterbots (really, robots of any kind!), and natural language processing. I used a markov chain generator to create this ipsum model (inspired by Garkov!).</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <p>You can add any Bowie song you like to the dictionary, as long as my code can grab the lyrics... this ipsum will learn from it. Look at a list of songs already in the dictionary here.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
